fields.name: Email
fields.description:
Contact Email. It is visible on the top of site page as an image to 
protect from spambot.

fields.name: Skype
fields.description: Contact skype. It is visible on the top of site page.

fields.name: Google Analytic code
fields.description: Code uses to connect to Google Analytic service.

fields.name: Max number of inner pages
fields.description:
Number of pages that can be shown under main menu when 
user follow links inside page. Generally inner pages used only as a link inside content.

fields.name: Turn on/off REST Api
fields.description:
Turn on/off alternative way of getting pages using REST api. Only a 
special marked pages can be available for api. For more information please look into page statuses list.

fields.name: Image quality
fields.description:
Global setting quality uploaded pictures. The picture quality 
is directly proportional to the size of the file. A value of 100 corresponds to the maximum quality.

fields.name: Phone number
fields.description:
Contact phone number. It is visible on the top of site 
page.

fields.name: Image autoscale
fields.description: Global setting for autoscale uploaded pictures if its width>333px. Pictures will be scaled to width=333px.
